{"tid":1463873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說 [鬼] , 試著說 [意見不合既手足]","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:02:24.000Z","uid":116034,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"288e1367299c1047b6c67da942dcb7755e9f9fac","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:48.000Z","msg":"自從發現有警察扮示威者<br />\n呢幾日既po/留言/說話裏面<br />\n呢個鬼字既出現率係勁多<br />\n一有咩意見不合 就懷疑人係鬼<br />\n<br />\n當第一印象就假定左果個人係鬼<br />\n你講出既言論唔只影響人地<br />\n仲影響埋你自己 形成種潛意識<br />\n<br />\n當我地潛意識認定左有鬼既存在<br />\n我地就會慌會擔心身邊既人出賣自己<br />\n呢個時候就正正中哂對家既圈套<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地之所以可以行到呢一步<br />\n(唔好話目標達成<br />\n但只少做左一種威脅/難題比對家)<br />\n係因為我地一直都信自己既伙伴 </span><br />\n<br />\n但而家對家正正係利用我地對人果種信任去同我地打心理戰<br />\n<br />\n所以我地正正應該時時保持頭腦清晰<br />\n我地正正係冇大台<br />\n人人都係獨立思考 每人做既決定會有機會唔同 <br />\n我地應該做既係首先冷靜理解佢地既做法<br />\n好好咁去溝通<br />\n而唔係一開波就話人係鬼<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗有排打咖大佬 我地自己都搞分化點得啊<br />\n保持一個強壯既心!!!!!<br />\n<br />\nps個人意見 唔個解釋得清唔清楚<br />\n<br />\n對準政權!!!!!!五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"ac88ac4c113b948b809b209d5d562ec8ed7fce2d","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4231b7661d349e8dd83a51f73d2564640a1193","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:34.000Z","msg":"加油!!!!!"},{"pid":"a26c3e405b15bae1485acbb3ea21749dcb129342","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"加油!!!!!"},{"pid":"487c943eeb9900422cfc8c8861a4edf18458aaa5","tid":1463873,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"58e924570812e5493d30ab5cf1469bdd811c78b4","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"加油!!!!!"},{"pid":"04f85977aea3d841836006149a18ab234476aa13","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9230763bfa1512788f421d0c7a1966b1efc2889a","tid":1463873,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"同意，用字真係好重要<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"5806ecf2aef4afaf13eb73b3d3fa546eb568adc5","tid":1463873,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:48.000Z","msg":"p牌出唔到多一個post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都想講，而家有人成日見人大大隻，或者女仔剪短髮就影相上黎話係鬼。結果好多都係真示威者，比人點相比人鬧。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好心大家最少問下對方，接觸完都覺得有可疑先再算。<br />\n<br />\n同埋鬼係捉唔曬，唔好太沉迷捉鬼遊戲。除非捉一隻殺一隻，唔係冇可能冇鬼。但當我地成日覺得所有野都係鬼左，而割蓆，我地就輸硬。<br />\n<br />\n打救護同打記者另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb9159f44c13fc461b200c3b6314f8ba6d55415","tid":1463873,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41965eead5b16798337fe61bc38a73e365aaa82e","tid":1463873,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5806ecf2aef4afaf13eb73b3d3fa546eb568adc5","tid":1463873,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:58:48.000Z","msg":"p牌出唔到多一個post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都想講，而家有人成日見人大大隻，或者女仔剪短髮就影相上黎話係鬼。結果好多都係真示威者，比人點相比人鬧。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好心大家最少問下對方，接觸完都覺得有可疑先再算。<br />\n<br />\n同埋鬼係捉唔曬，唔好太沉迷捉鬼遊戲。除非捉一隻殺一隻，唔係冇可能冇鬼。但當我地成日覺得所有野都係鬼左，而割蓆，我地就輸硬。<br />\n<br />\n打救護同打記者另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:59:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c568df1801883c3a0caaf41e589f76abf9fa0153","tid":1463873,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"不割席 不篤灰 不分化"},{"pid":"3b80d93c5e1c4d9395acd824563f47fc16e25624","tid":1463873,"uid":32352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:00:57.000Z","msg":"有咩意見唔同既 <br />\n有D你覺得係鬼既<br />\n就冷靜D同佢講"},{"pid":"492bc49ae8760a151fddf0f235cc4fbeeb22b4cc","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:01:24.000Z","msg":"加油啊大家!!!!!"},{"pid":"5896549c8976fbef840a981ccb978b8ae88d1874","tid":1463873,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:01:32.000Z","msg":"大家聽住。<br />\n知唔知點解政府811咁撚豬會畀你地影到示威者入面有鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而唔繼續鬼落去<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地呢招好撚高，政府知我地核彈都唔撚割。所以特登話你知：我地放咗鬼喺你度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等你次次都疑神疑鬼，等戰友間失去咗互相信任。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗吓，由612 走到而家，我地本住一句核彈都唔割先得。所以，所有檢討post，要等該日完咗先好出。仲有唔好懷疑自己身邊嘅人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰友總畀警鬼多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰、不分化、不足鬼<br />\n</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ad6bf7471601893192249ed843e3b98e3e3f1402","tid":1463873,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:02:06.000Z","msg":"不割席 不篤灰 不分化"},{"pid":"fb70ab86898d804a2fa3c45a7f9401618622e286","tid":1463873,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:03:00.000Z","msg":"不割席 不篤灰 不分化"},{"pid":"45d0e14acf90c6b5839f168c143da2868f22971b","tid":1463873,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"意見不合既手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好得意<br />\n<br />\n不割席 不篤灰 不分化!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7005bfba32017721f49ded32208af7d7a4f41d7","tid":1463873,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:04:08.000Z","msg":"咁共產黨係唔係意見不合既政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c989a020d699a1432a936120e6c719c698a69a9","tid":1463873,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d36037ce4be1012fb8fc9fad83ba6f3136166ce","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7005bfba32017721f49ded32208af7d7a4f41d7","tid":1463873,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:04:08.000Z","msg":"咁共產黨係唔係意見不合既政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"咁鬼係對家25仔<br />\n但手足即使意見不合 始終係自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4201567a2e34bd316eeb8bb2ea4f7fa78c59cdca","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6ab0c0d7790197289ee7626f66cf3a1afdf20a","tid":1463873,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"283dec818082147545e2a2446dbb686b908169d9","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:11:07.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n818百萬大遊行"},{"pid":"29712fad7b66691113332c48fb376d2fd4bceddd","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:11:17.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n818百萬大遊行"},{"pid":"fa74900d3c30f5b6c94b957d761662cec372be73","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:11:32.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n818百萬大遊行"},{"pid":"571ecea15bf6b970c54199f4ee93213c944cd5d6","tid":1463873,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"可以試下"},{"pid":"8f66c639440c880aecc3b608153f0c07f1c72d60","tid":1463873,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2abc91fe5f2b1503f4036085e58fd9df1eb84dab","tid":1463873,"uid":281966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">和而不同</span>，好嗎<br />\n大家出得黎，目標一致，只係手段不同"},{"pid":"40fb7f45a1c103494bf360156157b5bf73659f6e","tid":1463873,"uid":116034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n818百萬大遊行"},{"pid":"014b50930f995c40f965e556afc3a444cc54d332","tid":1463873,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"呢招我都係學你地架渣, 我發現屈人係鬼真係好撚爽, 我決定以後都屈班犬儒淆底獸係鬼"},{"pid":"e48cf07aa36a363d3429841e5233b0362acaa767","tid":1463873,"uid":34